name: MilwaukeeSanitation
0: ”Alexa, ask Milwaukee Sanitation when is garbage day”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: milwaukee sanitation
des:
This skill allows residents of Milwaukee, WI to ask Alexa when their garbage or recycling day is.

You will need to set your Alexa device's location in the Amazon Alexa app and grant permissions for this skill to retrieve your device's address.

This skill is not affiliated in any way with the city of Milwaukee Department of Public Works.

The information in this skill is retrieved directly from the city's website: https://itmdapps.milwaukee.gov/DPWServletsPublic/garbage_day
